#### text ####
text: After lunch it was off to Portland to visit cousins Gordon and Lisa. Both Dad and I had gotten into cycling since we last saw them and they're long-time avid cyclists, so we had a lot to talk about! I also enjoyed playing Chronology (created by a friend of theirs) and chatting about family history. (Mom was between eye surgery and getting new glasses)
