#### text ####
text: On the drive to Junction City, my parents indulged me by stopping at a bird sanctuary. Dad (who was doing all the driving) took a nap while mom took a fast walk and I took a slow walk looking for birds. I met a couple birders and had a nice chat and some bird tips!
