#### location ####
text: Indian Ford Meadow Preserve
----
lat: 44.326152199999996
----
lon: -121.53101919999999
#### text ####
text: While Mom and Carol explored and shopped around town, Dad and Don were kind enough to take me birding at Indian Ford Meadow Preserve and Calliope Crossing. It was pretty quiet, but we heard a loud flock of Wild Turkey go by in the woods, that disappeared when we went looking - impressive considering how big they are!
