#### location ####
text: William L. Finley National Wildlife Refuge
----
lat: 44.41313238475077
----
lon: -123.33213198690466
#### text ####
text: The next day, Dad and Don again kindly took me out birding, this time to William L. Finley NWR. We took the Woodpecker loop and sure enough found some woodpeckers. That loop also has a tremendous diversity of habitat! Fields and wetlands and multiple types of forest.
